{"tid":2041074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（衝破心理關口）每日任務，路過民賤聯街站屌廢老","createTime":"2020-05-29T04:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T09:05:23.000Z","uid":310423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43665b8cb1188abe4de83a1933b500f8cc27c4cd","tid":2041074,"uid":310423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:06:01.000Z","msg":"衝破心理關口 原來屌人係咁爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民賤聯專係朝早廢老時聯擺街站，而我又咁啱呢個時間返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日撚日叫人支持國安法，正一仆街賣港賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次行過屌一句，第二次經過竟然夠膽屌幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌完佢其實我都打哂冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但打冷震嘅點係好驚我再咁落去會變成電腦大爆炸阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269fe7ed8ac221fd670c9139500f83d5610931e9","tid":2041074,"uid":301067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾個叻你，我未夠膽好似藍絲咁做到人無恥便無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日好想屌但淆底"},{"pid":"d118c16ef266de48c55350806190274efdcec437","tid":2041074,"uid":310423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"269fe7ed8ac221fd670c9139500f83d5610931e9","tid":2041074,"uid":301067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾個叻你，我未夠膽好似藍絲咁做到人無恥便無敵<img src=\"/asse